-- Mitsubishi, Bic Camera to Agree to Alliance on Electric-Car Sales in Japan
-- B y   G o   O n o m i t s u
-- 2010-11-09T00:41:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-09/mitsubishi-bic-camera-to-agree-to-alliance-on-electric-car-sales-in-japan.html
Mitsubishi Motors Corp. and Bic
Camera Inc. agreed to cooperate on electric-car sales in Japan.  The electronics retailer will help promote Mitsubishi’s i-
MiEV electric car by organizing test drives and displaying the
vehicle, according to a statement today on the Japanese
automaker’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
